<p class="center" id="esspri">ESSPRI is developed as a simple index for measuring pSS patient's symptoms. The ESSPRI is calculated by averaging the scales for pain, fatigue and dryness.</p> <br>

<form action="/esspriscale" method="POST">
   <label for="dryness">Dryness Status (100-mm VAS)(0=not dry, 100=very dry):</label>
    <p class="range-field">
      <input type="range" id="dryness" name="dryness" min="0" max="100" />
    </p>
    <label for="fatigue">Fatigue Status (100-mm VAS)(0=no fatigue, 100=high fatigue):</label>
    <p class="range-field">
      <input type="range" id="fatigue" name="fatigue" min="0" max="100" />
    </p>
    <label for="pain">Pain Status (100-mm VAS)(0=no pain, 100=high pain):</label>
     <p class="range-field">
      <input type="range" id="pain" name="pain" min="0" max="100" />
      </p>
        <div class="row">
            <input type="submit" value="Submit" class="btn save"> 
            <a href="/dashboard" class="btn orange">Cancel</a>
        </div>
    </form>
  </form>

